Q-3. Write an SQL query to print the name of employees having the highest salary in each department.
A-3 :-  SELECT w.first_name, w.department, w.salary
        from worker w,
        (SELECT department, max(salary) max_sal FROM worker 
        GROUP BY department) dept_max_sal
        WHERE w.salary = dept_max_sal.max_sal
        And w.department = dept_max_sal.department;

